 <title>Changes &amp; Deprecated Functionality</title>

 <para>This chapter covers both major changes to existing functionality, and
 also deprecated and removed functionality.</para>

 <section xml:id="changes">
  <title>Major Changes to Existing Functionality</title>

  <para>If you are running older versions of the Gateway you must modify
  your <filename>config.json</filename>.</para>

  <para><literal>"type"</literal> entries no longer require the full Java
  package name. The <filename>config.json</filename> should no longer contain
  any Java package names. For example, change lines such as the
  following:</para>

  <programlisting language="javascript"
  >"type" : "com.apexidentity.filter.Chain"</programlisting>

  <para>When you remove the full Java package name, the resulting line is as
  follows.</para>

  <programlisting language="javascript">"type" : "Chain"</programlisting>
 </section>

